      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This vehicle is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-cared for, showing only the typical signs of light use you'd expect from a car that has been enjoyed and maintained responsibly. It runs smoothly and is ready to hit the road today!",
