    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, offering a dependable and comfortable driving experience. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear, such as small scratches and light dings, the interior remains clean and well-kept. All major systems are functional, making this a solid choice for anyone seeking a reliable vehicle that is ready for the road.",
