      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While the frame is intact, the engine currently has a major oil leak and the transmission shifts roughly. The exterior shows extensive wear, including several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and some rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and rear power windows, are non-functional. This car is being sold as-is and is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts.",
